=================
Program: fsniffer 
=================
* A simple flow sniffer roughly modeled after the argus tool.


======
Usage:
======
$ ./fsniffer [-r filename] [-i interface] [-t time] [-o time_offset] [-N num] [-S secs]

==========================
Building on DETER machines
==========================
To build on DETER machines g++48 needs to be used instead of the regular g++ command.
Running 'make deter' instead of 'make all' on a DETER machine will fix this issue.


======================================
Generate same output using argus tool:
======================================
$ argus -r opensafety_udp_trace.pcap -w output.argus
$ ra -r output.argus -s stime proto saddr sport dir daddr dport pkts bytes state dur


